{"tid":1930272,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"高盛：料中國首季GDP跌9% 全年增長3%","createTime":"2020-03-17T12:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-17T14:15:43.000Z","uid":228995,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"644ff889878e3106a536413fdaca3fcabda6c41c","tid":1930272,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:15:50.000Z","msg":"//受新型冠狀病毒肺炎（新冠肺炎）疫情影響，多間機構下調中國經濟按年增長預測。高盛最新發布報告，對中國今年第一季GDP增速預測，由之前增長2.5%，大幅調降至收縮9%，全年增長降至3%。<br />\n<br />\n高盛報告稱，中國官方今年1至2月經濟運行數據，以及3月至今的高頻指標表明，首季實際GDP增長，要比其先前預測的要弱得多。根據高頻跟蹤和行業水平分析，高盛料首季實際GDP下降9%。<br />\n<br />\n第三季前 GDP增長難恢復至疫情<br />\n<br />\n高盛認為，新冠肺炎疫情最近在其他國家迅速傳播，料第二季中國以外經濟體的增速將明顯放緩，在全球經濟疲軟的背景下，中國經濟活動的複蘇也可能受限。該行預計，在第三季之前，實際GDP都不會恢復到肺炎爆發前的增長趨勢。//<br />\n<br />\n得唔得啊？"},{"pid":"dbcda3485bd7ace61492f24f5899f9943ff93099","tid":1930272,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:16:32.000Z","msg":"贏到開巷"},{"pid":"645c51c91168311b533badf6c9fdfb5c8fbc362e","tid":1930272,"uid":333163,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:19:56.000Z","msg":"簡單數學<br />\n<br />\n(-9 + 3x )/4 = 3<br />\n<br />\nx = 7<br />\n<br />\n之後每季最少要按年有 7% 增長<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97f73e210ea8dc2b7ee7bfb030610d0d904046d8","tid":1930272,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:22:48.000Z","msg":"保6"},{"pid":"74dca2548d6254621ab031532e0c6f9a996ed09d","tid":1930272,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"645c51c91168311b533badf6c9fdfb5c8fbc362e","tid":1930272,"uid":333163,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:19:56.000Z","msg":"簡單數學<br />\n<br />\n(-9 + 3x )/4 = 3<br />\n<br />\nx = 7<br />\n<br />\n之後每季最少要按年有 7% 增長<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:34:22.000Z","msg":"你嘅數學係支那係唔適用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"916bf08c76870370f917ac178e1f859bb57b499e","tid":1930272,"uid":326712,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"645c51c91168311b533badf6c9fdfb5c8fbc362e","tid":1930272,"uid":333163,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:19:56.000Z","msg":"簡單數學<br />\n<br />\n(-9 + 3x )/4 = 3<br />\n<br />\nx = 7<br />\n<br />\n之後每季最少要按年有 7% 增長<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T13:14:48.000Z","msg":"第二季都死啦之後兩季點止7%"},{"pid":"5934580bc1c7e960c846e37a2856df21182eb464","tid":1930272,"uid":333163,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"916bf08c76870370f917ac178e1f859bb57b499e","tid":1930272,"uid":326712,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"645c51c91168311b533badf6c9fdfb5c8fbc362e","tid":1930272,"uid":333163,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T12:19:56.000Z","msg":"簡單數學<br />\n<br />\n(-9 + 3x )/4 = 3<br />\n<br />\nx = 7<br />\n<br />\n之後每季最少要按年有 7% 增長<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hk